  "text": "The Envoy ADS (Aggregated Discovery Service) gRPC client implementation is located in source/extensions/config_subscription/grpc/. The implementation consists of several key components: (1) **gRPC Stream Handlers**: GrpcStream (grpc_stream.h) and GrpcStreamInterface (grpc_stream_interface.h) manage the bidirectional gRPC communication with the xDS server. GrpcMuxFailover (grpc_mux_failover.h) provides failover support between primary and secondary xDS servers. (2) **Main ADS Client Implementation**: GrpcMuxImpl (grpc_mux_impl.cc/h) is the legacy ADS client that manages subscriptions and handles the StreamAggregatedResources RPC. NewGrpcMuxImpl (new_grpc_mux_impl.cc/h) is the delta-xDS specialized version using DeltaAggregatedResources. The xds_mux/grpc_mux_impl.h provides a unified template-based implementation with GrpcMuxDelta and GrpcMuxSotw specializations for both delta and state-of-the-world modes. (3) **Resource Subscription Tracking**: WatchMap (watch_map.cc/h) manages subscriptions to xDS resources, tracking which resources multiple clients are interested in and deduplicating requests to the server. (4) **Delta-xDS State Machine**: The delta-xDS protocol state is tracked in two locations: legacy DeltaSubscriptionState (delta_subscription_state.cc/h) and the newer xds_mux/DeltaSubscriptionState (xds_mux/delta_subscription_state.cc/h). Similarly, state-of-the-world is handled by SotwSubscriptionState (xds_mux/sotw_subscription_state.cc/h). Both extend BaseSubscriptionState (xds_mux/subscription_state.h) which provides common protocol state management and resource handling. (5) **ACK/NACK Processing**: PausableAckQueue (pausable_ack_queue.cc/h) manages the queue of acknowledgments to be sent back to the server, handling the head-of-line blocking issue when certain resource types are paused. UpdateAck (update_ack.h) represents individual ACK/NACK messages with nonce, type_url, and error details. (6) **Supporting Components**: GrpcSubscriptionImpl (grpc_subscription_impl.cc/h) and various factory classes handle subscription lifecycle. GrpcMuxContext (grpc_mux_context.h) aggregates configuration and dependencies. EdsResourcesCacheImpl (eds_resources_cache_impl.cc/h) caches endpoint discovery service resources for performance. XdsSourceId (xds_source_id.cc/h) identifies xDS resources. The entire ADS implementation converges on the DiscoveryRequest/DiscoveryResponse (and DeltaDiscoveryRequest/DeltaDiscoveryResponse for delta mode) protocol messages from envoy.service.discovery.v3 package."
}

